                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1630</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you create a builder from an instance and then use the .getXxxBuilder() method you get an empty builder instead of a builder than contains the data elements from the original instance.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
